Class Tier1sFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.tier_1s.Tier1sFactory

  • public class Tier1sFactory
extends Object
    Tier1sFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.tier_1s package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
